::KitKat::
While running, she opened her link to Dollen and GoldenEye,"Hey 
Dollen, GoldenEye, Magatron has planned an ambush and he is cloning 
warriors.  Starscream is there now and already fighting. I need you 
two over there at the old base as fast as you can. I'm headed there 
now. Don't hide, just fire on the slagging pieces of scrap."

GoldenEye::
She got KitKat's message. "Oh great, Megatron's cloning. I just hope 
that were not too badly out numbered."
She transformed back into eagle mode and flew off towards the base.
